<a id="top"> </a><h1>Postdoctoral Fellowship, University of Calgary</h1>
<p>
The Department of Philosophy at the University of Calgary invites 
applications for a one-year postdoctoral fellowship starting on 
September 1, 2012. The area of specialization is logic or the philosophy 
of science. The fellow will be expected to have a well-defined research 
project, teach up to one course each term, and participate in the 
research activities of the Department. All requirements for the PhD must 
have been completed by the starting date and no earlier than September 
2007.  The stipend is $50,000 Canadian per year. 
</p>
